## SS 10. Create Regular Post (Text Only)

### Step 1: Open modal (SS 8), wait 2s

### Step 2: Type post text

Replace `${postContent}`.

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { var host = document.querySelector('#interop-outlet'); var shadow = host.shadowRoot; var editor = shadow.querySelector('.ql-editor[role=\"textbox\"]') || shadow.querySelector('[contenteditable=\"true\"][role=\"textbox\"]'); if (!editor) return { success: false, reason: 'no-editor' }; editor.focus(); var lines = '${postContent}'.split(String.fromCharCode(10)); editor.innerHTML = lines.map(function(line) { return '<p>' + (line.trim() === '' ? '<br>' : line) + '</p>'; }).join(''); editor.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true })); return { success: true, length: editor.innerText.length }; }"}
ENDJSON
```

